headline: Generac Promotes Amanda Teder to Chief Marketing Officer
summary: Generac Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: GNRC), a leading global designer, manufacturer and provider of energy technology solutions and other power products, today announced the promotion of Amanda Teder to Chief Marketing Officer. Amanda previously served as Executive Vice President of Marketing.
